01:05:56.639 --> 01:06:03.760
being fair to them or putting them under pressure just for my own fun. That's not it. The job is,

01:06:04.719 --> 01:06:10.320
it's Friday night and we're playing Saturday and our coach says, hey, I'm struggling with

01:06:10.320 --> 01:06:16.159
